{"context":"처음 만나서 인사하며","dialogue":[{"speaker":"A","text":"처음 뵙겠습니다!","romanization":"cheoeum boepgesseupnida!","translation":"Nice to meet you (formal, first time)!"},{"speaker":"B","text":"안녕하세요! 만나서 반갑습니다.","romanization":"annyeonghaseyo! mannaseo bangapseupnida.","translation":"Hello! Nice to meet you."},{"speaker":"A","text":"저도 만나서 반가워요.","romanization":"jeodo mannaseo bangawoyo.","translation":"Nice to meet you too."},{"speaker":"B","text":"오늘 날씨가 좋네요!","romanization":"oneul nalssiga jotneyo!","translation":"The weather is nice today!"}]}